I"ü <p>A comprehensive list of apps I use + apps I have to keep record of because I may need them, but not right now. Sub-elements in the lists are links to great learning resources (official documentation, if present, won‚Äôt be mentioned). Everything is free and Open Source, except where otherwise specified.</p>

<p>Right now on my MacBook Pro 13‚Äù 2019:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/exp/firefox/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Mozilla Firefox</a>, the best browser ever.</li>
