  <li><a href="https://blockstack.org/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Blockstack</a>, ideally, it‚Äôs something <strong>awesome</strong>, definitely game-changing. Practically, it doesn‚Äôt work on my Mac (I tried <a href="https://forum.blockstack.org/t/cant-use-any-dapp/10628" rel="noopener" target="_blank">everything</a>).</li>
  <li><a href="https://kevin-de-koninck.github.io/Clean-Me/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Clean Me</a>, an Open Source, better, neat and perfectly working alternative to CCleaner written in Swift.</li>
